ss=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kuk1665702812056.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kuk1665702812056.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kuk1665702812056.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kuk1665702812056\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                      \n Tags\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Tags are shortcuts to ProcScript modules. The Tags pane lists the tags available in the current trigger.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__section_w112ab1b5b1_w113ab1b5_w114ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__section_gv1_vgg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d203482e56\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__ul_ngd_wgg_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__li_d3503e1_d3504e1_d3505e1\">Double-click a tag to navigate to the beginning of the\n          associated trigger or entry. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__li_d3506e1_d3507e1_d3508e1\">To add, delete, or clear tags, select the tag, trigger,\n          or entry and choose the appropriate menu item from the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span> menu or\n          context menu. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__section_o5j_wgg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d203482e74\">Icons</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Meaning of Tag Icons</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__1\">Icon </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__2\">Meaning </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__3\">Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__fig_vw3_xgg_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Standard tag\" class=\"image\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__image_ww3_xgg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_tagstd.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__2\">Tag </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__3\">Marks the beginning of a trigger or entry. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__fig_xw3_xgg_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Manual tag\" class=\"image\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__image_yw3_xgg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_tagper.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__2\">Manual Tag </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__3\">Manually-added tags. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__fig_zw3_xgg_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Tag for compilation error\" class=\"image\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__image_ax3_xgg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_tagerr.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__2\">Compilation Tags </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__3\">Tags automatically added by the compiler when it\n                encounters an error in the ProcScript. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__fig_bx3_xgg_5cc\">\n<img alt=\"Find tag\" class=\"image\" id=\"kuk1665702812056__image_cx3_xgg_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_tagfin.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__2\">Find Tag </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kuk1665702812056__table_d605e1_d606e1_d607e1__entry__3\">Tags marking triggers or operations that contain the\n                specified search string. <p class=\"p\">To search in triggers, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File&gt;Find in Triggers</span></span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420886\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420886\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tags Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Tags Tags are shortcuts to ProcScript modules. The Tags pane lists the tags available in the current trigger. How to Double-click a tag to navigate to the beginning of the associated trigger or entry. To add, delete, or clear tags, select the tag, trigger, or entry and choose the appropriate menu item from the Edit menu or context menu. Icons Table 1. Meaning of Tag Icons Icon Meaning Meaning Tag Marks the beginning of a trigger or entry. Manual Tag Manually-added tags. Compilation Tags Tags automatically added by the compiler when it encounters an error in the ProcScript. Find Tag Tags marking triggers or operations that contain the specified search string. To search in triggers, choose File>Find in Triggers . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}